data.description: Searching for the perfect ranch home near the Fox Chain-O-Lakes? LOOK NO FURTHER! Welcome to your dream single-level, 3 bedroom/1 bath retreat by Pistakee Lake! As you step inside, you'll be welcomed by a spacious living/dining room combo, bathed in natural light streaming through the large BAY WINDOW. Enjoy all STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES in the well-appointed kitchen. Dream of relaxing evenings in the large family room, complete with a vaulted ceiling and a BRICK FIREPLACE. The family room opens up to a back deck with views of Pistakee Lake and of the expansive, FULLY FENCED backyard.   Situated in close proximity to the highly sought-after Fox Chain-O-Lakes, water enthusiasts will find endless opportunities for recreation and relaxation. Additionally, easy access to Route 12 ensures stress-free commutes for work or play. Don't miss the chance to make this single-level ranch-style gem yours! View the Virtual 3D Tour to preview the home easily.
